high_descs: Turn to the right and face the stove.
Pick the fork up from the counter.
Go to the left and stand in front of the white cup on the counter.
Put the fork into the cup on the counter.
Pick the cup up from the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the cup down in front of and on the left side of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the fork to the right of the sponge.
Turn around and walk to the counter that has the mug on it.
Place the fork inside of the mug.
Pick up the mug with the fork in it.
Turn left and walk to the microwave cart on the right, turn right to face the microwave.
Put the mug down in front of the tomato on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork in front of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the counter.
Pick up the fork to the right of the sponge.
Turn around, then walk to the counter towards your right.
Place the fork in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn left and walk until you get to the microwave on your right.
Place the mug on the left side of the counter with the microwave on it, in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a fork in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left
Pick up a fork off of the kitchen top
Turn to your right and face the kitchen top
Drop the fork in the mug on the counter top
Pick up the mug with the fork in it
Turn left and then turn to your right at the microwave
Put the mug with the fork in it down on the black counter top
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with the fork in it down on a black counter top
